name: [CX] - SOCAR Booking Start in 20 Minutes Car DFZ >200m

parameters.query:
=SELECT Lower(email)          AS email,
       INITCAP(display_name) AS NAME
FROM   users
WHERE  uuid='{{ $json.user_id }}'

SET timezone = 'Asia/Kuala_Lumpur';
SELECT *
FROM   (SELECT ref_no                                          AS id,
               user_id                                         AS UID,
               listing_id                                      AS cid,
               TO_CHAR(request_start_at, 'dd-MM-IYYY HH:MIam') AS start_time,
               CASE
                 WHEN delivery.fee IS NOT NULL
                      AND pickup.fee IS NOT NULL THEN 'both'
                 WHEN delivery.fee IS NOT NULL THEN 'delivery_only'
                 WHEN pickup.fee IS NOT NULL THEN 'pickup_only'
                 WHEN chauffeur.fee IS NOT NULL THEN 'SOCAR+'
                 ELSE 'Round'
               END                                             AS service_type
        -- Booking
        FROM   bookings b
               -- Delivery
               left join (SELECT booking_id AS bid,
                                 amount     AS fee
                          FROM   booking_lines
                          WHERE  status = 'success'
                                 AND name = 'Delivery Fee') AS delivery
                      ON delivery.bid = b.id
               -- Pickup
               left join (SELECT booking_id AS bid,
                                 amount     AS fee
                          FROM   booking_lines
                          WHERE  status = 'success'
                                 AND name = 'Pick Up Fee') AS pickup
                      ON pickup.bid = b.id
               -- Chauffeur
               left join (SELECT booking_id AS bid,
                                 amount     AS fee
                          FROM   booking_lines
                          WHERE  status = 'success'
                                 AND name = 'Chauffeur Fee') AS chauffeur
                      ON chauffeur.bid = b.id
        WHERE  b.status = 'accepted'
               AND b.net_amount <> 0
               AND ROUND(( EXTRACT(epoch FROM b.request_start_at - NOW()) / 60 )
                         ::
                         DECIMAL, 2)
                   BETWEEN 0 AND 20) AS temp
WHERE  ( service_type != 'both'
         AND service_type != 'delivery_only' )
